{
  "info": {
    "name": "KOSMO API v3 — Complete",
    "description": "Colección completa y optimizada de KOSMO API — sin endpoints duplicados, sin endpoints legacy inexistentes.\n\n## Organización\n\nEjecutar en orden dentro de cada carpeta. Las variables se auto-propagan entre requests.\n\n0. Health — sanity check\n1. Auth PKCE S256 — Register → Authorize → Token → Refresh → Me → Logout\n2. Proyectos — CRUD + estado del wizard\n3. Discovery — Documento enriquecido (9 secciones, índice de navegación, IA)\n4. Features — Generar, sugerir, crear, aprobar, mejorar, eliminar\n5. Requisitos EARS — Documento enriquecido por feature (6 categorías, IA)\n6. Preferencias — Listar, ajustar confianza, eliminar\n7. Utilidades — Schemas JSON, OpenAPI, Spec viewer\n\n## IDs\n\nULID con prefijo tipado: prj_ (project), feat_ (feature), spec_ (spec), usr_ (user), pref_ (preference).\n\n## Errores\n\nRFC 7807 Problem Detail (Content-Type: application/problem+json).\n\n## Pre-requisitos\n\n- Servidor: uv run uvicorn kosmo.infrastructure.api.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000\n- O Docker: docker compose up -d (PostgreSQL + Redis + MongoDB + Backend)\n- .env con LLM_PROVIDER configurado (noop para dev, deepseek para prod)\n- Usuario seed: uv run python -m kosmo.infrastructure.scripts.seed_dev_user",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "email", "value": "dev@kosmo.dev", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "dev-password-12345", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "user_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "project_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "project_slug", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "feature_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "preference_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "spec_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Health",
      "description": "Verificar que el servidor responde.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Health Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('status = ok', function () { pm.expect(pm.response.json().status).to.eql('ok'); });"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/health", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Auth (PKCE S256)",
      "description": "Flujo OAuth 2.1 + PKCE completo. Ejecutar en orden: Register → Authorize → Token. El access_token y refresh_token se guardan automáticamente en variables de colección.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1.1 Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) { pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value); if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) pm.environment.set(key, value); }",
                  "pm.test('201 o 409', function () { pm.expect([201, 409]).to.include(pm.response.code); });",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) { var body = pm.response.json(); setVar('user_id', body.id); console.log('Usuario creado:', body.id); } else { console.log('Usuario ya existe (409) — OK'); }"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.2 Authorize (PKCE S256)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function b64url(wordArray) { return CryptoJS.enc.Base64.stringify(wordArray).replace(/\\+/g, '-').replace(/\\//g, '_').replace(/=+$/g, ''); }",
                  "var verifier = b64url(CryptoJS.lib.WordArray.random(48));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('code_verifier', verifier);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('code_challenge', b64url(CryptoJS.SHA256(verifier)));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) { pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value); if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) pm.environment.set(key, value); }",
                  "pm.test('201 Created', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json(); setVar('authorization_code', body.authorization_code);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\",\n  \"code_challenge\": \"{{code_challenge}}\",\n  \"code_challenge_method\": \"S256\",\n  \"scopes\": [\"agent:run\", \"profile:read\"]\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/authorize", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "authorize"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.3 Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) { pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value); if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) pm.environment.set(key, value); }",
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "setVar('access_token', body.access.token);",
                  "setVar('refresh_token', body.refresh.token);",
                  "if (body.subject) setVar('user_id', body.subject);",
                  "console.log('Tokens obtenidos. Subject:', body.subject, '| Expires:', body.access.expires_at);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"grant_type\": \"authorization_code\",\n  \"code\": \"{{authorization_code}}\",\n  \"code_verifier\": \"{{code_verifier}}\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "token"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.4 Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) { pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value); if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) pm.environment.set(key, value); }",
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "setVar('access_token', body.access.token);",
                  "setVar('refresh_token', body.refresh.token);",
                  "console.log('Tokens rotados. Nueva familia.');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"grant_type\": \"refresh_token\",\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.5 Me (get Principal)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Tiene subject y scopes', function () { pm.expect(body.subject).to.be.a('string'); pm.expect(body.scopes).to.be.an('array'); });",
                  "console.log('Principal:', body.subject, '| Scopes:', body.scopes.join(', '));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.6 Logout",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('204 No Content', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(204); });",
                  "console.log('Sesión revocada.');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/logout", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "logout"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Proyectos",
      "description": "CRUD de proyectos. Los proyectos inician en fase 'descubrimiento'. IDs con prefijo prj_. Slugs auto-generados desde el nombre. Soporte dual: ID y slug en todas las rutas.",
      "item": [
